*Briga* se ne isplati - (It's not worth the hassle.)
Niko mu ne može pomoći u *brigama* - (Nobody can help him with his troubles.)
On se nije brinuo o *brigama* - (He didn't worry about troubles.)
Ona se ne opterećuje *brigama* - (She doesn't bother with troubles.)
Niko ne može pobegnuti od *brige* - (Nobody can escape from worry.)